<CDLItem itemNbr="33-44-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.CDL.3-33-44-01.1.3-33-44-01">
<Title>Anti-collision Tail Light Assembly</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any number may be missing. The associated position light and anti-collision light
system must be considered inoperative</Para>
<Note>
<Para>When the lens is missing, disconnect electrical power and remove position light and anti-collision light LED modules, lens and lens housing. With the rest of the light assembly intact, cover the opening with speed tape.</Para>
</Note>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must be dispatched using MEL items 33-43-01 and 33-44-01.</Para>
</Note>
